{"build_type":"library","description":"Walk a dependency-graph entry list (each entry is {package, kind, defines:[names], calls:[names]} as produced by build_package_dependency_relation_graph) starting at 'entry', following .next. For each entry whose array field named 'fieldname' (either 'calls' or 'defines') contains 'symbol', append the entry's package name to the 'out' string array. Field-parameterized so one scan serves both callers (field=calls) and defined_in (field=defines). Package-granular: it answers which PACKAGE references the symbol, not which function. Reuses json_string_array_contains_value + encode_textual_payload_document_value.","module_name":"collect-graph-packages-whose-field-lists-symbol","package_name":"collect-graph-packages-whose-field-lists-symbol","function_definitions":{"collect-graph-packages-whose-field-lists-symbol":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"entry","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"fieldname","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"symbol","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"out","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_package","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"package"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"entry"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"locate-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"entry"},{"kind":"var","value":"fieldname"}],"result_assignment_variable":"fieldarr","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"count-members-inside-container-value","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"fieldarr"}],"resul